data.text:
This week on Movie Caboose Kris and Liana sit down to have a chat about rappin' Warren Beatty's white guilt political comedy, Bulworth (1998). Starring Warren Beatty, Halle Berry, Oliver Platt, Paul Sorvino, and a huge cast of others.

Which actor will be chosen from Bulworth to link us to next week's movie? You'll have to listen to find out.

If you would like to help us pick the next episode's movie, please go to our socials and leave a movie suggestion for us to talk about next week.
